ulaneum.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 0aCivilization, Classical. 0aMaterial culturezItalyzHerculaneum (Extinct city) 0aMaterial culturezItalyzHerculaneum (Extinct city). 0aMaterial culturezItalyzNaples, Bay of. 0aMaterial culturezItalyzPompeii (Extinct city) 0aMaterial culturezItalyzPompeii (Extinct city). 0aWomenzItalyzHerculaneum (Extinct city) 0aWomenzItalyzHerculaneum (Extinct city). 0aWomenzItalyzPompeii (Extinct city) 0aWomenzItalyzPompeii (Extinct city). 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aCaldwell, Lauren, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDamer, Erika Zimmermann, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aD’Ambra, Eve, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEmmerson, Allison L. C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGazda, Elaine K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJacobelli, Luciana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKellum, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaird, Margaret L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLevin-Richardson, Sarah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLongfellow, Brenda, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLongfellow, Brenda, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPetersen, Lauren Hackworth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPowers, Jessica, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSwetnam-Burland, Molly, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSwetnam-Burland, Molly, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relato